N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 5200.3 - Transfer of calls

State Regulations
A PSAP shall transfer all wireless 911 calls originating
outside its jurisdiction to the appropriate agencies pursuant to existing local
practice. Notes
